edBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHello<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec84e27fa661e359d845b8c71e97632f1a25a4e","tid":11024,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a65647452c294abbb510a530fb25b63edafa7f7","tid":11024,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"咬大棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa77e764a727898218faf4f68e96d47196ec6f56","tid":11024,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講明先我唔知你改左呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開頭就諗住用個侵字"},{"pid":"48a0b9a60d78f604dec081ec5072418d032777c1","tid":11024,"uid":17262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"陳柏宇 <br />\n<br />\n你瞞我瞞<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：陳光榮<br />\n編曲：陳光榮<br />\n監製：陳光榮<br />\n<br />\n約會像是 為分享到飽肚滋味<br />\n有任何難題 卻不提起<br />\n<br />\n這若是浪漫 我怎麼覺得就快分離<br />\n妳哭過 但眼影閃得更艷美<br />\n<br />\n我是誰情人 妳始終也是妳<br />\n微笑靜默互望 笑比哭更可悲<br />\n<br />\n就算怎開心皺著眉<br />\n儘管緊緊抱得穩妳<br />\n兩臂 卻分得開我共妳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無言的 Donald Trump 侵襲我心<br />\n然而希拉里講 我累得很</span><br />\n<br />\n如除我以外 在妳心 還多出一個人<br />\n妳瞞住我 我亦瞞住我 太合襯<br />\n<br />\n這就是談情 客氣得嚇著我<br />\n除了近來繁忙 我所知有幾多<br />\n<br />\n若要哭 不哭訴為何<br />\n大家 爭吵鬥嘴好過<br />\n勝過笑不出聲 抱著我<br />\n<br />\n這麼寂寞的戀愛 算甚麼<br />\n用妳指尖纏我 用熱吻逃避我"}]}